29 six rebounds, and Santez Pendleton added 25 points, 19
30 rebounds, and eight assists; Devonte Penn added 13 points,
31 and Demazzia Taylor scored 11; and
32 WHEREAS, the Wenonah High School Boys Basketball Team
33 has been coached and inspired by Head Coach Cedric Lane and
34 his staff; under their leadership, the players have
35 broadened their knowledge of the game, refined their skills
36 in execution, and established a school tradition of superior
37 play and true sportsmanship; and
38 WHEREAS, the dedication of the entire roster,
39 coaching staff, and the Wenonah community has brought great
40 honor to the City of Birmingham and the State of Alabama;
41 and
42 WHEREAS, the Wenonah High School Boys Basketball
43 Team's success is a tremendous source of pride for their
44 families, classmates, teachers, administrators, and the
45 entire community, whose dedication and support have played a
46 crucial role in motivating the team; now therefore,
47 BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE
48 LEGISLATURE OF ALABAMA, That the Wenonah High School 2026
49 Boys Basketball Team and coaches are highly honored and
50 commended on winning the AHSAA 5A State Championship Title,
51 and we hereby dedicate this resolution to them in utmost
52 admiration, along with best wishes for continued success.
